# SN Video Upscaler

Windows desktop app that upscales videos with **Google Colab GPU**.

This repository is being built up in small, reviewable PRs. Today the
`main` branch only contains this README.

## Roadmap

- **PR #1** — Project setup + Windows desktop app skeleton.
- **PR #2** — Final UI/UX layout.
- **PR #3** — Google Colab worker notebook.
- **PR #4** — Desktop ↔ Colab connection.
- **PR #5** — Single video upload → process → download.
- **PR #6** — Batch queue, one-by-one.
- **PR #7** — Polish, error handling, Windows EXE packaging, README, QA.

See open PRs for the current work in flight.
